; Coverage for compare.cc: amount comparison in sort

2024/01/01 Big
    Expenses:Food    $20.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/02 Small
    Expenses:Food    $5.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg Expenses --sort amount
24-Jan-02 Small                 Expenses:Food                 $5.00        $5.00
24-Jan-01 Big                   Expenses:Food                $20.00       $25.00
end test
